The process aims to separate the three fractions through several unit operations, including:
Cooking;
Pressing/Centrifugation;
Decantation;
Drying.

Omega-3 FAs can be present in several forms in supplements, including:
Natural TAGs;
Ethyl esters;
Re-esterified TAGs enriched in ω-3 Fas;
Free fatty acids;
Phospholipids.
